  "instructions": [
    "Peel and dice the avocado into small cubes.",
    "Chop green bell pepper, onion, and garlic finely. Set aside.",
    "Heat olive oil in a non-stick pan over medium heat.",
    "Add vegetable shortening to the pan and swirl to coat evenly.",
    "Once melted, add red pepper flakes and saut\u00e9 for 30 seconds.",
    "Add diced avocado, green bell peppers, onion, and garlic. Stir-fry until vegetables are soft and fragrant.",
